text: The 1999 Qatar Crown Prince Cup was the 5th edition of this cup tournament in men's football (soccer). It was played by the top four teams of the Q-League. Al-Wakrah were crowned champions for the first time. ==Results== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center; margin: 0 auto;" |- !1999 Qatar Crown Prince Cup Winners |- | Al-Wakrah 1st Title |} Category:Qatar Crown Prince Cup Category:1998–99 in Qatari football
